{"tid":590941,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"英雄聯盟算唔算開創左大電競時代","createTime":"2018-03-13T05:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T12:04:43.000Z","uid":36134,"like":12,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3fffe46352e8ea5551e27474f60eafd8fe295fbe","tid":590941,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"當初 s3定s4<br />\n睇到riot一篇文話要將lol打造成世界級既賽事（已經做到）<br />\n仲要申辦入奧運  個陣聽到呢句 <br />\n真係想恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但而家諗返<br />\n電競行業確實朝住呢個方向發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係東亞運動會有項目<br />\n我覺得已經係好驚人既成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加上呢幾年我觀察<br />\nLol成熟既職業體系 選手收入同待遇<br />\n都大大改變左好多人對電競既睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我感覺如果無lol成功既電競模式<br />\n電競未必有今日既發展<br />\n而且一定緩慢好多"},{"pid":"4d652b669590cd1f796890167bf2f2aba7917c78","tid":590941,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:45:55.000Z","msg":"當然我所謂既大電競時代都係誇張左d<br />\n吸引下眼球咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ba48c370dea7baa5b32da9aaa5711944640cf1","tid":590941,"uid":46155,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:46:46.000Z","msg":"魔獸撚不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f98928264eefe545ec93d3b054bdef12a2d9473","tid":590941,"uid":98570,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:47:52.000Z","msg":"走阿樓主 陣間又有班信長撚出黎屌你嫁喇"},{"pid":"d19ce2bc9246417533c88bc5fd813b9c5a73929a","tid":590941,"uid":761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:48:31.000Z","msg":"信長狗快d咬樓主"},{"pid":"71dcf9f82361192dd2502f4461d583dfa0d92b2c","tid":590941,"uid"